    "This aspect has been relatively underexplored, as it is tightly coupled with downstream tasks.",
    "Finally, managing speaker turns and preserving correct sequential order in multiparty conversations remain open problems that warrant further investigation.",
    "Building on the challenges discussed in Section VIII, as Speech LLMs continue to evolve, addressing key challenges will be crucial for their progress.",
    "Two primary issues that warrant focused research are instruction sensitivity and the degradation of semantic reasoning abilities.",
